---
<section id="about" class="p-8">
  <SectionPage>
    <p class="text-4xl font-medium">About</p>
    <p class="text-2xl opacity-50">Engineer by trade, problem solver by nature</p>
    <div class="mb-12"></div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <Avatar url='https://github.com/mcsamuelshoko/readme/blob/main/src/images/freelancer-profile.png?raw=true' />
        <div class="md:col-span-2 px-8 bg-primary text-white rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl lg:rounded-4xl p-8 text-lg place-content-center ">
          <p class="max-w-xl">
            Beyond code, I am a Graphic designer who values both purpose and appearance. I combine my technical skills with design thinking to create great solutions. I enjoy building lasting products that solve real problems. <br>
            <br>
            When I'm not building software, you'll find me: <br>
            — Exploring emerging tech trends and best practices <br>
            — Learning from engineering podcasts and conference talks <br>
            — Designing digital products and experiences <br>
            — Gaming and creating content to stay creative <br>
            <br>
            My approach is pragmatic: write maintainable code, solve real problems, and keep learning. I want my work to hit hard and make a difference.
          </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="my-12 px-8 flex flex-wrap space-x-8 space-y-8">
      <a target="_blank" href={SOCIAL_URLS.wakatime}><img src={wakatimeIconUrl} alt={'wakatime icon'} title={'visit ' + ' wakatime profile'} class='h-12 lg:h-16' /></a>
